metadata.name: TAKE ME INTO METAVERSE
metadata.description:
I've been through many tragedies, I've been through many events, 
I've been through a lot of ups and downs, while working on this project, 
sometimes I think "is this real?" , "is this really happening?" ,
 sometimes I think "what if I live in a digital world?", 
but I have to return to real life, life is not like the world of metavers, 
life is real.
.
I present to you a work of art created using digital tools,
"TAKE ME INTO METAVERS"
The details tell the tragedy that I have gone through while make this Digital art.
.
2160x3840 High Resolution.MP4
With Original Sound.Mp3
>3D Animation<
1/1 Art by Jztye.
